class TreeNode:

    def __init__(self, val=0, left=None, right=None):
        self.val = val
        self.left = left
        self.right = right

def findGreaterValues(root):
    count = 1
    result = []

    def inorderTraversal(node):
        nonlocal count
        if node:
            inorderTraversal(node.left)
            count += 1
            result.append(count)
            inorderTraversal(node.right)
    inorderTraversal(root)
    return result
